title: Per-Sopdu
description: Ancient Egyptian town that was the capital of the 20th nome of Lower Egypt and was a major cult site, dedicated to Sopdu, the god of the eastern borders of Egypt. The site is now under the modern town of Saft el-Hinna.

properties.description: Point based on an OpenStreetMap node representing Per-Sopdu after Wikidata.
